#. type: delimited block + 4
#: content/en/releases/4.4R/errata.adoc:49
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"        <p>This errata document contains ``late-breaking news''\n"
"        about FreeBSD 4.4-RELEASE. Before installing this version,\n"
"        it is important to consult this document to learn about any\n"
"        post-release discoveries or problems that may already have\n"
"        been found and fixed.</p>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block + 4
#: content/en/releases/4.4R/errata.adoc:59
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"        <p>Any version of this errata document actually distributed\n"
"        with the release (for example, on a CDROM distribution)\n"
"        will be out of date by definition, but other copies are\n"
"        kept updated on the Internet and should be consulted as the\n"
"        ``current errata'' for this release. These other copies of\n"
"        the errata are located at <a href=\n"
"        \"http://www.FreeBSD.org/releases/\" target=\n"
"        \"_top\">http://www.FreeBSD.org/releases/</a>, plus any sites\n"
"        which keep up-to-date mirrors of this location.</p>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block + 4
#: content/en/releases/4.4R/errata.adoc:63
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"        <p>Source and binary snapshots of FreeBSD 4-STABLE also\n"
"        contain up-to-date copies of this document (as of the time\n"
"        of the snapshot).</p>\n"
msgstr ""

